'''巴德尔·乔巴瓦'''（{{lang-ka|ბაადურ ჯობავა}}，{{bd|1983年|11月26日}}），[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]][[国际象棋|国际象棋]]棋手、[[国际象棋特级大师|特级大师]]。

乔巴瓦曾于2003年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ratings.fide.com/tournament_report.phtml?event16=24484 |title=FIDE Archive - Tournament report July 2003: GEO 63rd Champ |publisher=FIDE |date= |accessdate=2011-12-18 |archive-date=2014-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327220056/http://ratings.fide.com/tournament_report.phtml?event16=24484 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、2007年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chesscenter.com/twic/twic646.html#6 |title=The Week in Chess 646 |publisher=Chesscenter.com |date= |accessdate=2011-12-18 |archive-date=2008-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080217040719/http://www.chesscenter.com/twic/twic646.html#6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、2012年<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nikoladze|first1=Sopho|title=Jobava wins Georgian Championship with 2½ point lead|url=http://en.chessbase.com/post/jobava-wins-georgian-championship-with-2-point-lead|publisher=ChessBase|accessdate=6 January 2016|date=2012-05-28|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103425/http://en.chessbase.com/post/jobava-wins-georgian-championship-with-2-point-lead|dead-url=no}}</ref>三度获得格鲁吉亚国际象棋全国冠军。其最高[[等级分|等级分]]为2012年9月创下的2734分。

